<br>
Some boy (12-14) picked my son up (5) and slammed him against the wall of the school building.  Upon asking my son what he did, my son stated &quot;duhhh daddy I feigned death til he stopped camping me&quot;.<br>
<br>
Of course he missed his bus, had a bloody nose, and scared the crap out of a teacher that walked by to see a boy laying lifeless bleeding through his nose.  <br>
<br>
Try explaining what feign death is to a schools principal.  All in all, I think his skill is maxed, being that the teacher &quot;thought&quot; he was dead.  Imagine her surprise when he looked up to &quot;see&quot; why she was screaming.  Only thing that sucks is the bully got a 3 day vacation out of it, I wanted the 3 say vacation.<br>
<br>
Thank god he plays a monk, I'd hate to see what would have happened if he had played a mage instead and thought &quot;I'll cast my pet&quot; (though I am sure he wouldn't have tried since he didn't have any malechite on him). <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=yizanpetpimpin>Yizan Pet Pimpin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 12<br> <font color=#333333>(11/11/02 6:03:40 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergoofystuff.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=205.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home1.gte.net/res0rg9w/tomoanim3.gif width=100 height=125></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Confused Youth</span><hr size=1> The sick twisted side of me cant help but laugh about this.<br>
